## Patch: add write-failure cleanup regression scaffold

```powershell
Describe "RetrievalCache Priority 0 regressions" {
    BeforeAll {
        . "$PSScriptRoot/../module/LLMWorkflow/retrieval/RetrievalCache.ps1"
    }

    It "Preserves the original write failure when temp cleanup also fails" {
        # This is an integration-oriented scaffold.
        # Intended future setup:
        # 1. force Write-CacheFile to fail after temp file creation
        # 2. force Remove-Item on the temp file to fail
        # 3. assert the thrown error is still the cache write failure
        # 4. optionally assert a warning was emitted for temp cleanup failure

        { Write-CacheFile -CacheFile (Join-Path $TestDrive 'cache.jsonl') -Entries @() } | Should -Not -Throw
    }
}
```

